## Homebrew (macOS / Linux)

```bash
brew tap {{HOMEBREW_TAP}}
brew install {{TOOL_NAME}}
```

## pipx (recommended for isolated install)

```bash
pipx install {{TOOL_NAME}}
```

## pip

```bash
pip install {{TOOL_NAME}}
```

## PyPI

Latest release: [pypi.org/project/{{TOOL_NAME}}](https://pypi.org/project/{{TOOL_NAME}})

## Prebuilt binary

Download from [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/{{GITHUB_USER}}/{{TOOL_NAME}}/releases).
Available for macOS (amd64/arm64) and Linux (amd64/arm64).

## Verify

```bash
{{TOOL_NAME}} version
```
